**who —** King Hippo — the giant from Hippo Island — jab his open mouth to make him drop his guard, then hit the exposed belly to tear off the bandage; once knocked down he cannot rise

**what —** the giant from Hippo Island — jab his open mouth to make him drop his guard, then hit the exposed belly to tear off the bandage; once knocked down he cannot rise

