**why —** He is the purest puzzle in the gallery: an enormous wall with one sequence of openings, and a body that, once it falls, stays down.

**how —** Crystallized from Mike Tyson's Punch-Out!! (NES 1987) / the arcade Punch-Out!! (1984).

**◌ the mythos —** He is the purest puzzle in the gallery: an enormous wall with one sequence of openings, and a body that, once it falls, stays down. a being of the ring, the read, and the climb to the Dream Fight

